---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for loveoverexile.com — how we collect, use, and protect your data."
  noIndex={true}
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow prose">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: 28 February 2026</p>

      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how Love Over Exile ("we", "us", "our") collects,
        uses, and protects your personal data when you visit loveoverexile.com or use
        our services.
      </p>
      <p>
        We take your privacy seriously. This site serves a sensitive audience — parents
        experiencing parental alienation — and we handle your data with the care and
        discretion that requires.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
      <p>
        Love Over Exile is operated by Malcolm Smith. For data protection purposes, Malcolm
        Smith is the data controller for this website.
      </p>
      <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:info@loveoverexile.com">info@loveoverexile.com</a></p>

      <h2>2. What data we collect</h2>
      <h3>When you sign up for the waitlist or community</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>First name (optional)</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>When you use the contact form</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Name</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Message content</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Automatically collected</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Analytics data (page views, traffic sources, device type) via Google Analytics 4</li>
        <li>IP address (anonymised)</li>
        <li>Browser and device information</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How we use your data</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To send you the free Survival Guide and community notifications you requested</li>
        <li>To send our newsletter (only if you have opted in)</li>
        <li>To respond to contact form messages</li>
        <li>To understand how the site is used and improve it (analytics)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell your data. We do not use it for advertising targeting.</p>

      <h2>4. Legal basis for processing (UK/EU)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Consent</strong> — for email marketing and the community waitlist</li>
        <li><strong>Legitimate interests</strong> — for analytics and security</li>
        <li><strong>Contract</strong> — for processing contact form messages</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Third-party services</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>MailerLite</strong> — email marketing (EU GDPR compliant)</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> — website analytics (anonymised IP)</li>
        <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — website hosting (EU data centres available)</li>
        <li><strong>Discourse</strong> — community forum (self-hosted)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
      <p>Under UK GDPR and applicable law, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time (including unsubscribing from emails)</li>
        <li>Object to processing</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@loveoverexile.com">info@loveoverexile.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        We use cookies for analytics purposes (Google Analytics). You can disable cookies
        in your browser settings. We will display a cookie consent notice in accordance
        with UK/EU law.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        Email subscribers: data retained until you unsubscribe or request deletion.
        Contact form messages: retained for up to 2 years.
        Analytics data: retained per Google Analytics default settings (14 months).
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. The date at the top of this page
        will always show when it was last updated.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For any data protection questions or requests:
        <a href="mailto:info@loveoverexile.com">info@loveoverexile.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.last-updated {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--color-warm-grey);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
</style>
